metadata.name: Walks Of Life
metadata.description:
Looking at things from a different perspective when all else fails tear the walls down.  
Theres alot to been seen on the other sideüñ§  
With each wall you tear down, you'll have a better understanding of what's really going on. Many times, the walls we build up can limit our perspective, so it's important to take the time to explore new perspectives. By tearing down the walls, you can get a better idea of what the situation is, and figure out a better way to approach it.
